import React from 'react'
import { Card, Icon } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const description = [
  'Bob is a violinist with 2 years experience in the wedding industry.',
  'He enjoys the outdoors and currently resides in upstate New York.',
].join(' ')

const CardExampleExtraContent = () => (
  <Card color="teal">
    <Card.Content header='About Bob' />
    <Card.Content description={description} />
    <Card.Content extra>
      <Icon name='user' />
      200 Friends
    </Card.Content>
  </Card>
)

export default CardExampleExtraContent;
